notes: Iraq-KRI (Sulaymaniyah) profiling exercise of urban/out-of-camp IDPs, Syrian refugees, and host populations with data collected June 2016 (report published September 2016). The exercise included a household survey administered to a sample of 1,201 households (401 IDP, 401 refugee and 399 host community households). Data can also be explored through the DART: http://www.dart.jips.org/.
